				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The biggest disadvantage of 8x16 sprites is that they have more minimum blank space. This means bullets and the like will take up more space in your pattern table, and things will start hitting the 25% sprite overdraw limit and flickering earlier. And if you're using MMC3's scanline counter, the unique ability of 8x16 sprites to draw from both pattern tables becomes useless.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

